Fourth Department,

November, 1957

(September 18, 1957)* The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Daniel Askew, Amended to Lavender Tinch, Appellant.

Not published with other decisions of Sept. 18, 1957, 4 A D 2d 848, Sept. 23, 1957, 4 A D 2d 851, and Nov. 8, 1957, 4 A D 2d 997.— [Rep.

Motion to amend record on appeal denied. Memorandum: The motion papers show that an order to amend the record has already been made by the Erie County Judge.
